sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Agent as Exception-Handler-Agent
    participant ErrorAnalyzer
    participant SolutionRecommender
    participant LearningSystem
    participant Escalation as Escalation-Team

    User->>Agent: Report exception/unusual case
    activate Agent
    Agent->>ErrorAnalyzer: Analyze exception
    activate ErrorAnalyzer
    ErrorAnalyzer-->>Agent: Analysis result
    deactivate ErrorAnalyzer

    Agent->>SolutionRecommender: Request solution proposals
    activate SolutionRecommender
    SolutionRecommender-->>Agent: Suggested solutions
    deactivate SolutionRecommender

    alt Solution applicable
        Agent-->>User: Provide solution
        Agent->>LearningSystem: Log case & outcome
        activate LearningSystem
        LearningSystem-->>Agent: Update complete
        deactivate LearningSystem
    else No viable solution
        Agent->>Escalation: Escalate case
        activate Escalation
        Escalation-->>Agent: Escalation response
        deactivate Escalation
        Agent-->>User: Inform about escalation
        Agent->>LearningSystem: Log escalation & outcome
        activate LearningSystem
        LearningSystem-->>Agent: Update complete
        deactivate LearningSystem
    end
    deactivate Agent